ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to Moravian Indian Reserve No. 47, Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart 0.363 hectare (0.897 acre), more or less, including mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Moravian of the Thames Band as an addition to MORAVIAN INDIAN RESERVE NO. 47, located in the rural Municipality of Chatham-Kent approximately 56 kilometres from the City of Sarnia, Ontario.
